=== Regular commands ===

Double quote string: "hello world"
Single quote chars: 'hello world'
Backtick chars: `hello world`

=== IF comparisons ===

Single quote comparison works
Double quote comparison works

=== FOR /F without usebackq ===

Double quoted string: test
Single quoted command: cmd
Backtick filename: file

=== FOR /F with usebackq ===

usebackq double: test
usebackq single: literal
usebackq backtick: backtick

=== Filenames with quotes ===

content
content

